    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions like @Compendium[pf1.spells.53dyu81yaw4y0nz4]{Glyph of Warding}, except that a <em>greater blast glyph</em> deals up to 10d8 points of damage, and a <em>greater spell glyph</em> can store a spell of 6th level or lower.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf1.spells.j0bc0iii8zp1jiwr]{Read Magic} allows you to identify a greater <em>Glyph of Warding</em> with a DC 16 @Compendium[pf1.skills.uLZI2uWz0uB8UgBc]{Spellcraft} check.</p>\n<p><em>Material Component</em>: You trace the glyph with incense, which must first be sprinkled with powdered diamond worth at least 400 gp.</p>",
